snippet.title: Champion Unmasked: Lex Luthor
snippet.description:
When humanity is caught in the middle of a multidimensional Crisis, who do you call? Superman? No! This looks like a job for Lex Luthor.

Do you want to step into the shoes of humanity's savior? Download and play Infinite Crisis for FREE today at http://www.infinitecrisis.com.
